{
  "id": "69f7bfb35e7a53be43539c5b",
  "title": "2026/03/28―atohs",
  "created": 1777844148,
  "updated": 1777844153,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb35e7a53be43539c5b",
      "text": "2026/03/28―atohs",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c4e",
      "text": "from [2026/03/28]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844150
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c50",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c51",
      "text": " 日記が長くなりがちなので、ネストが増えてきたら積極的に別ページに切り出していこう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c52",
      "text": "  と、今はそう思っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c53",
      "text": " 高速バスでPC作業をするのが苦手",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c54",
      "text": " \t酔う？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c55",
      "text": " \tノートPCの画面が小さく感じる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c56",
      "text": " \tさっさと諦めた方が良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c57",
      "text": " 何もしてないのに警告された",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c58",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/f0481ffdc41d06562744676fb3460aa2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c59",
      "text": "  \t航空法に怒られるってどんな状況[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5a",
      "text": " 今日は[ハイエース]を運転します",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5b",
      "text": "  でかい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5c",
      "text": "  バッグ駐車がもともと苦手なのに、もっと難しい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5d",
      "text": "  　窓いっぱいついてて視界はすごくいいので、慣れると逆にハイエース以外でバック駐車できなくなる…[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5e",
      "text": "  　 車体が長いデバフが強すぎて、慣れていないとやはり無理でした……[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c5f",
      "text": "  本当にこの車幅でこの道路通っていいのかといちいち不安になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c60",
      "text": "  ご安全に[terang.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][nyarla.icon][meganii.icon][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c61",
      "text": " 乗り終えた！ 応援ありがとうございました！！！！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c62",
      "text": " 他の人の日記読むのは[誤配]的な文脈で捉えられるのだろうか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c63",
      "text": "  真面目に[あずまん]を読む時が来たかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bfb300000000002a8c64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844148,
      "updated": 1777844148
    },
